%%{init: {"sequence": {"mirrorActors": false}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as Kanban Board
    participant API as Task API
    participant Rules as State Machine
    participant WS as WebSocket
    participant DB as Database
    participant Log as Activity Log

    User->>UI: View board
    UI->>API: GET /api/tasks?projectId=X
    API->>DB: Fetch tasks grouped by status
    DB-->>API: Tasks by column
    API-->>UI: Render Kanban columns

    User->>UI: Drag task from "Todo" to "In Progress"
    UI->>UI: Optimistic UI update
    UI->>API: PATCH /api/tasks/{id} {status: "In Progress"}
    API->>Rules: Validate transition (Todo → In Progress)

    alt Valid Transition
        Rules-->>API: Allowed
        API->>DB: UPDATE task SET status, updatedAt
        par Persist & Broadcast
            API->>Log: INSERT activity {from: Todo, to: In Progress}
            API->>WS: Broadcast to project room
        end
        WS-->>UI: Other users see card move
        API-->>UI: Success
    else Invalid Transition
        Rules-->>API: Blocked (e.g., Done → Todo)
        API-->>UI: Error: Invalid state transition
        UI->>UI: Revert drag position
    end

    User->>UI: Drag to "In Progress" column
    UI->>API: GET /api/columns/{id}/count
    API->>DB: Count tasks in column
    DB-->>API: count: 8, limit: 8

    alt count < limit
        API-->>UI: Drop allowed
    else count >= limit
        API-->>UI: Warning: WIP limit reached (8/8)
        UI->>UI: Show limit warning overlay
    end
